# General 9Anime Fixes
# Average user experence fixes (Fixes the website)
@@||9anime.*$~third-party,domain=9anime.to|9anime.ru|9anime.live|9anime.one|9anime.love|9anime.life|9anime.tv|9anime.page|9anime.video

# Fix for certain videos never loading, mostly on mobile but it may cause issues on personal computers too.
# This also resolves certain stylesheet issues, wherein it wouldn't load the css file.
@@||*.akacdn.ru$domain=9anime.to|9anime.ru|9anime.live|9anime.one|9anime.love|9anime.life|9anime.tv|9anime.page|9anime.video|prettyfast.to

# Ensuring the recaptcha api always loads
@@||google.com/recaptcha/*$domain=9anime.to|9anime.ru|9anime.live|9anime.one|9anime.love|9anime.life|9anime.tv|9anime.page|9anime.video|prettyfast.to
